			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="- Go to Kurwin Coffin&#xD;&#xA;- Find the child in the upper graveyard, near the house&#xD;&#xA;- Dig up the grave by the child&#xD;&#xA;- Feel all the guilt in the world&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;Bookmark: larian://bookmark?name=CTY_KurwinCoffin&amp;mod=GustavDev&amp;level=CTY_Main_A&amp;camPos=3.885604;42.978622;30.843765&amp;camTarget=4.312797;42.531807;30.057722" />
